# 🚀 Why AI Matters

Artificial Intelligence is changing how software is built.

Modern applications are expected to:

* Understand user intent
* Answer questions
* Search large amounts of information
* Generate content
* Automate repetitive work
* Assist decision making
* Improve user experiences

Rather than replacing traditional software engineering, AI extends its capabilities.

